4 Honorable Rodolphe Sambou, is a passionate fan of Les Rouge-et-Bleu; and
5 WHEREAS, Paris Saint-Germain Football Club is most deserving of the highest
6 recognition for winning European soccer's most-prestigious prize: the UEFA Champions
7 League Trophy.
8 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
9 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Paris Saint-Germain Football Club on
10 winning its second consecutive UEFA Champions League title and does hereby extend
11 sincerest wishes that club continue to prosper in all of its competitive endeavors for many
12 more years to come.
